    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing around 60 species of herbs and shrubs native to Europe, North Africa, and parts of Asia, but widely introduced elsewhere. Several species have become popular garden flowers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
